{"tid":224281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"假冒漁護處外判職員捉狗 偷運中國供食用","createTime":"2017-05-01T02:31:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-01T17:54:06.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fa51c37177f95a2fea8a16d55d4cd099dae2355f","tid":224281,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T02:31:40.000Z","msg":"｜壹週Plus｜Next Plus<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20150429/large/1430310550_8407.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20150429%2Flarge%2F1430310550_8407.jpg&h=6556c680&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本月初深水埗驚爆懷疑有人劏狗案，今日再有報導指，有人假冒漁農處外判職員，在打鼓嶺坪洋村捉流浪狗，懷疑有人將之販賣回中國供人食用。<br />\n<br />\n據報導指，上月有坪洋村居民發現，有兩名男子於村內用套索及捕獸籠捉走一隻黑色流浪狗；當時有查問兩名男子身份，但對方聲稱是漁護署外判職員。之後兩星期再有聲稱是漁護署外判捉狗隊，並捉走另一隻流浪狗。不過，漁護處從來沒有外判捉狗工作，亦沒有到坪洋村的捉狗紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n有狗房老闆指，一直有人從事水路走私狗隻的活動，並在流浮山一帶不時有舢舨偷運中國病狗來香港出售，同時亦偷運一些三個月大的狗仔回中國，供人食用，而且每隻可賣六七百元。"},{"pid":"e29b00494f053abde9d4ca17c03b2d94f53ce243","tid":224281,"uid":31237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T02:36:41.000Z","msg":"做一個完整的中國人是愛吃狗肉的"},{"pid":"f2b45491f09afa96d4d218722292b1396907a21f","tid":224281,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T02:38:46.000Z","msg":"唔好意思原來係舊聞嚟，見facebook貼以為係新新聞，單新聞係2015年"},{"pid":"33be29a00b3b5b4bb9be087f52daa6ac32f56ec8","tid":224281,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T03:20:05.000Z","msg":"中國冇狗咩要落香港捉咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa59a28840ff02206f3daf7d3d08861d23845639","tid":224281,"uid":71133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T03:25:50.000Z","msg":"話唔定係連登仔黎，要幫d豬牛雞報仇"},{"pid":"eca84d6c6122ca7f6147e7558917f4d83503a3f3","tid":224281,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T03:27:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d30d3aaa4d34af4599ac0205fafa8aac31d89e4e","tid":224281,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T03:29:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bf1a817a71d1033fe122896d5e9fac76f114cca5","tid":224281,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T04:05:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做一個完整的中國人是愛吃狗肉的</blockquote><br />\n做一個完整的中國人是愛看TVB的"},{"pid":"f0f562f2076bfba3c888ee5ca452de3621d231b6","tid":224281,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T04:41:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d6b8af1702e7b65847fbc3f764c6ef032333fd16","tid":224281,"uid":38461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T11:45:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中國冇狗咩要落香港捉咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港咩多好啲嫁嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1a722924e5505b0db46450953b5330415896024","tid":224281,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T12:02:38.000Z","msg":"多謝支那專材"},{"pid":"7fc0c5d82a5d11c4df362d4a1ad56b84add6f308","tid":224281,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T17:54:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中國冇狗咩要落香港捉咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港咩多好啲嫁嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔多信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}